</taxonomicName>
CBS 141840T 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="75">a</emphasis>
colonies from left to right (top row) CYA, MEA, YES and OA; (bottom row) CYA reverse, MEA reverse, DG 18 and CREA 
